             (Police-constable S 165). I took the prisoner, and have the money, which is marked.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. The money was marked after he found it on me.</p>
               <p>MR. PITMAN. No; it was not.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 12.</p>
